                <head>289. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>At its 47th meeting on May 26, the informal working group on Antarctica agreed
                    that the conference for the drafting of an Antarctica Treaty would open at
                    Washington on October 25. (Memorandum of discussion; Department of State,
                    Central Files, 702.022/5–2659) For text of the press release announcing the
                    decision, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, June 2, 1959,
                    page 895.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
